data.description: Welcome home to Huron Circle, a large 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located on a corner lot in the gated community of Brighton Lakes. Huron Circle boasts 1,922 square feet and features a sprawling split floor plan. As soon as you approach the home, you are welcomed with the attractive covered entrance, heigh ceilings, natural light, and updated vinyl flooring throughout the home. Huron features a front living and dining space, rear breakfast nook and family room, and views of the patio and fenced in yard. The kitchen features updated modern white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, matte black hardware, and pantry.     The large Master Suite features a ceiling fan, private patio entrance and updated Ensuite with dual vanity sinks, soaking tub, walk in shower, and an abundance of storage space. The additional bedrooms are also large in size, feature their own closet space, and shared updated bathroom.    The main feature of this home is the rear covered lanai, raised patio, and fenced in backyard. This is the perfect space to relax, entertain friends and family for holidays, grill, and host gatherings. When you are not hosting, there is no doubt you won’t be exploring the community’s playgrounds, large pool, splash zone, tennis and basketball court, and more. Just 30 minutes away you will find Disney World, Animal Kingdom, ESPN Wide World of Sports, Epcot and Disney Springs. Welcome home!
